高等輸送現象                             ADVANCED TRANSPORT PHENOMENA


  	高等輸送現象This course will discuss the basic principles and applications of momentum, heat, and mass transfer in the area of chemical engineering from microscopic and macroscopic viewpoints. Other topics include dimensional analysis, scaling techniques, moving boundary problems, boundary layer theory, microfluidic transport, etc.

課程教育目標 

A 厚植專業知識與應用能力 Enhance professional knowledge and application skill/abilityB 強化獨立思考及創新研發能力 Strengthen independent thinking and innovative research and development 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

A 專精之化工知識及開發前瞻技術之能力。

D 結合化工專業知識與跨領域技術以發展新興科技之能力。

H 終身學習成長之能力。


